wing the study of the spectral behaviour\nand the physical processes acting on them. We also present the basic procedure\nto apply the method in maps convolved with asymmetric beams. The algorithm\ntakes ~ 72 hours for the most CPU time demanding channel (857 GHz) in a Compaq\nHPC320 (Alpha EV68 1 GHz processor) and requires 4 GB of RAM memory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Dec 2002 13:01:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 May 2003 16:02:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
