or new physics ideas.\n  As we want to treat a large amount of data and many models, computer\ntechnology constitutes an important part of our activity. We have concentrated\non the elaboration of artificial intelligence decision-making algorithms, as\nwell as on the delivery of computer tools for the end-user. Further linkage\nwith existing databases, such as PDG, COMPAS, and HEPDATA is being developed or\nplanned.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Dec 2002 21:03:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
